                                    >Bridging Open Work Permit (BOWP)</strong
                                > (if you applied for PR via Express Entry) or a new
                                close work permit supported by the nomination.
                            </div>
                        </details>

                        <details
                            class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 open:border-blue-200 open:shadow-md transition-all"
                        >
                            <summary
                                class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-slate-900 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none"
